name: Dell PowerVault MD3220i - 24 x 600GB 10k SAS
description:
Dell PowerVault MD3220i Storage Array

  • 24 x 600GB 10k 6G SAS 2.5" Dell Enterprise Class HDD
  • 14.4TB Raw Capacity
  • 2 x 1Gbps iSCSI Redundant Controllers 2GB Cache
  • x24 way backplane for up to 24 x 2.5" SAS or SAS SSD hard drives
  • Dual Redundant 600W PSUs
  • Rails Included
  • Bezel Not Included

  • 2 x iSCSI 1Gbps Redundant Controllers
  • 4 x iSCSI RJ45 IN 1Gbps Ethernet Ports Per Controller
  • 1 x SAS SFF-8088 OUT Per Controller
  • 1 x RJ45 1Gbps Management Port
  • 1 x Micro USB Port

The MD3220i can use MD1200 and MD1200 series expansion boxes to obtain a maximum of 192 hard drives.
Ideal for entry-level storage consolidation in virtualized environments.
Up to 8 servers can be directly connected to a single MD3220i Array, or up to 32 servers when configured with Ethernet switches.
